projects all the time,

218
00:09:44,834 --> 00:09:45,835
know what I mean?

219
00:09:45,835 --> 00:09:47,087
‐ I'm confused.

220
00:09:47,087 --> 00:09:49,297
Do you like biology
or don't you?

221
00:09:49,297 --> 00:09:50,965
‐ Well, if you want
to know the truth,

222
00:09:50,965 --> 00:09:52,550
